com.docusign.androidsdk.disposables

Class CompositeDisposableHandler

  • com.docusign.androidsdk.disposables.CompositeDisposableHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDisposableHandler

    public class CompositeDisposableHandler
implements IDisposableHandler

    A class that handles implementing the DisposableHandler interface. This interface allows adding the Disposable to a CompositeDisposable and then clearing it up. Any class wanting to manage Disposables can do so by delegating it to this class. See LoginViewModel as an example.
